Package: krsp
Title: Working with the Kluane Red Squirrel Project Database
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: c(
  person("Matthew", "Strimas-Mackey", email="mstrimas@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Andrew", "McAdam", email="amcadam@uoguelph.ca", role = c("aut", "cph"))
  )
Maintainer: Matthew Strimas-Mackey <mstrimas@gmail.com>
Description: This package is designed to help user bring data from the KRSP
    database into R. In addition, common database queries are standardized as R
    functions to ensure consistency.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.2),
    dplyr (>= 0.7.1)
